article.description: — Robbie Avila had 18 points in Indiana State's 98-54 victory against Southern Indiana on Saturday.
article.headline: Avila scores 18 as Indiana State knocks off Southern Indiana 98-54
article.linkText: Avila scores 18 as Indiana State knocks off Southern Indiana 98-54
article.story: TERRE HAUTE, Ind. -- — Robbie Avila had 18 points in Indiana State's 98-54 victory against Southern Indiana on Saturday. Avila added five rebounds and five assists for the Sycamores (9-1). Jaden Daughtry added 15 points and 11 rebounds. Ryan Conwell also scored 15 points. It was the eighth victory in a row for the Sycamores. Jeremiah Hernandez finished with 16 points for the Screaming Eagles (2-9). AJ Smith added 12 points and two steals for Southern Indiana. Ryan Hall also had nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
